parted
    getAllDisks()
    getDisk("/dev/sda")

    methods needed for converting types (numbers) to names (strings), or
    maybe store it all as a hash table and do lookups

    properties:
        list of all types (see partedUtils.py in anaconda)
        all constants from _ped need to be exposed here

    class Disk:
        properties:
            path          "/dev/sda"
            type          7
            model         "Micropolis Aphex Twin Signature Edition"
            length        32984729432
            sectorSize    2
            ...           (merge properties from _ped.Disk and _ped.Device)

            list of Partitions

        calling __init__ on Disk will probe for all Partitions, which in turn
        probe for all FileSystems

        methods:
            getLastPartitionNum()
            getPrimaryPartitionCount()
            check()
            label(...)                        type or guess based on arch
            getPartition(...)                 by sector, extended, path, or num
            getAllPartitions([type=XXX])
            sync()
            addPartition(...)
            removePartition(...)
            removeAllPartitions(...)
            getMaxPartitionSize(...)
            minimizeExtendedPartition(...)
            beginExternalAccess()
            endExternalAccess()
          ? getMaxLogicalPartitions()
          ? getMaxPrimaryPartitionCount()
            removePartitionTable(...)
            commit(...)

    class Partition:
        properties:
            path          "/dev/sda47"
            type          6
            disk          Disk object that owns this Partition
            number        3
            fileSystem    FileSystem object (or None)
            geometry      Geometry object
            active (rw)   True/False
            flags         or'ed list of flags
            system        special flag or part of flags?
            busy (ro)     True/False

        __init__(disk=Disk, fs=FileSystem, geom=Geomtry, flags=XXX, system=?)

        methods:
            getMaxGeometry(Constraint)

    class Geometry:
        properties:
            device (ro)   _ped.Device
            start
            length
            end

        methods:
            intersect(Geometry)
            testOverlap(Geometry)
            testInside(Geometry)
            testEqual(Geometry)
            testSectorInside(long int)
            read()
            write()
            sync()
            check()
            map()
